---
title: Pork Fillet with New Potatoes and Tarragon Sauce
description: Simple is best in this dish. Creamy and comforting, this delicious recipe from our Head Chef Andre is the perfect thing for chilly evenings at home. Tarragon, stock, and sour cream are gently combined to create a velvety sauce that works brilliantly with golden pan-fried pork steaks, buttery leeks and new potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-fillet-wk39-600b86f4-90d2730e.jpg
